br />\n個人認為兩樣都睇有啲重複"},{"pid":"a4c63919e2342a5a2e87b58935b744b39f9b1120","tid":231434,"uid":75657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T22:35:33.000Z","msg":"台場whole day?<br />\n我怕你後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw去台場可以搭水上巴士<br />\n好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe39aba6d990f5aaaa486c20d56cfa6e7dd51a5","tid":231434,"uid":75657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T22:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台場whole day?<br />\n我怕你後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw去台場可以搭水上巴士<br />\n好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最好D2果日去埋<br />\n1700到入去<br />\n搭水上巴士<br />\n喺上面吹住海風 夕陽天色 過埋條彩虹橋<br />\n行陣街 浸埋個大江户 咁就1 day"},{"pid":"660f51e18efe1988c6e410e31f5b50eab0958856","tid":231434,"uid":75657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T22:40:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>台場whole day?<br />\n我怕你後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw去台場可以搭水上巴士<br />\n好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最好D2果日去埋<br />\n1700到入去<br />\n搭水上巴士<br />\n喺上面吹住海風 夕陽天色 過埋條彩虹橋<br />\n行陣街 浸埋個大江户 咁就1 day</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gotokyo.org/tc/tourists/info/access/access5.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gotokyo.org%2Ftc%2Ftourists%2Finfo%2Faccess%2Faccess5.html&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2tibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=4f0337b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gotokyo.org/tc/tourists/info/access/access5.html</a><br />\nFor your reference"},{"pid":"c0264124861c9b18ac6edbeb2d2d6070dc94dc11","tid":231434,"uid":75657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T22:54:10.000Z","msg":"Day 5 可以考慮下 伊豆東（行下條城崎海岸線 ) 或者係 輕井澤 (踩下單車 行下outlet)<br />\n<br />\n睇你係咩類型人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c